orial director. Executive fashion director and columnist <strong>Rory Satra=
n</strong> got a bump, too. (Perhaps not in title, but responsibility.) Now=
 I hear that Lipsky-Karasz and <strong>Alex Fisher</strong>, the mag=E2=80=
